                            <img src="resource/images/image6.png" alt="adasda" class="image-sizing">

                            <p>The Navigator’s output to this query is:</p>

                            <img src="resource/images/image5.png" alt="adasda" style="width: 480px">

                            <p>This in turn informs me that the exactly the same indicator was also part of the MDGs
