                                <li>From your active Google Sheet, select “Get add-ons” from the top “Add-ons”
                                    menu.
                                </li>
                                <li>Search for "Joined-up Data Standard Navigator spreadsheet tool"</li>
                                <li>Click on '+ FREE'</li>
                                <li>Sign in to your Google Account if prompted</li>
                                <li> Review the summary of add-on’s requirements and select 'Allow'.</li>
                                <li>JUDS Navigator spreadsheet tool’ is now available in your 'Add-on' dropdown menu
                                    within your
                                    Google Sheet.
                                </li>
                            </ol>

